snippet.title: Keiser Report | The Legal & Moral Code Now Justifies Plunder | E1782
snippet.description:
In this episode of #KeiserReport, Max and Stacy look at the mass looting sweeping America as the legal and moral code now allows it. 

In the second half, Max chats to Aleks Svetski of Amber.app about his thoughts on the #hyperbitcoinization in El Salvador.
